description:
Geomi sup aka Spider Forest

"A noirish psychological suspenser wrapped around a murder mystery." -Vaniety 

Deep in the forest, a man and woman have been brutally attacked in a cabin and left to die.  Arriving too late, Kang (Gam Woo-sung) chases the killer only to be hit by a speeding car.  Barley surviving surgery, he know finds himself a prime suspect in a double murdercase.  While the investigation sets out to confirm his story, he cannot shake the feeling that there are strange gaps in his memory regarding that night in question and the killer's identity.  As he is piecing together the fragments of a bizarre dream, his own mightmares may hold the key to the truth.  

"Equal parts Horror, Murder Mystery and Detective Thriller." -BeyondHollywood.com

Actors: Seo Jeong-min, Son Byeong-ho, Kang Gyeong-heon, Jang Hyeon-seong, Gam Woo-seong
Directors: Song Il-gon
Language: Korean
